text: Aslayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Mindyaksky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 39 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 100 km from Uchaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Aslayevo, Uchalinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
